          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A highly segmented 4-pi detector system,",
                "the Plastic Ball detector (PB), consisted of phoswich",
                "modules built from a 4 mm CaF2 crystal and a 356 mm",
                "plastic scintillator. The plastic scintillator acts as",
                "a light-guide for the thin CaF2 crystal.",
                "In the centre of the PB is equipped with another",
                "segmented 2-pi-detector system, the Inner Shell",
                "detector (IS), consisting of 5 cm thick CsI(Tl)",
                "scintillators.",
                "The Heavy Ion detector(HI)-for the detection and",
                "identification of ions with 4 < Z < 6 and typical",
                "energies of 10-43 A*MeV, a specially designed array of",
                "phoswich scintillators in a segmented layer.",
                "The Big-Bite Spectrometer (BBS)-is a QQD-type magnetic",
                "spectrometer."
              ]
            }
          ],
